{"about_the_game":"<strong>A bullet hell with its own set of mechanics and unique bosses.</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enter the world of Vodos and fight demons and evil spirits. <br></li><li>Save the world from the evil clutches of the mad wizard Osilis.<br></li><li>Play as one of two characters with their own unique strengths.</li></ul><br><strong>But this is more than just your ordinary bullet hell.</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your spell abilities and increase your health as you progress.<br></li><li>In story mode, Your progress gets saved and you can retry bosses without having to restart the entire level.<br></li><li>Encounter unique and interesting bosses, with dialog that changes based on how you play.<br></li><li>Choose between an easy or hard route in story mode.<br></li><li>Play challenge levels, which are more difficult and have their own side story.<br></li><li>Collect cards that are chock-full of lore and useful hints.<br></li><li>Uncover dark secrets that will shake your moral fortitude.<br></li><li>Gameplay oriented, with fewer distractions and gimmicks than most other shoot-em-ups.<br></li><li>No curving bullets or screen shaking while dodging bullets.<br></li><li>Retro themed graphics, reminiscent of classic game consoles.<br></li><li>Has a killer soundtrack with both 8-bit and modern versions.</li></ul><br><strong>Magic has a purpose.</strong><br>You can be set on fire, frozen, cursed, and more.<br><br><i>Warning: This game has flashing lights and special effects that may be harmful to you if you have photosensitive epilepsy or a similar condition.</i><br><br><strong>Enjoy!</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mage in Training","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1910490/52e8f8892c70dc4dc84c1aec28f05996d28dea70.jpg"},{"name":"Go for the Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1910490/280abc1b82fbf568281e6c72e688d4926ddadabe.jpg"},